#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nancumprod.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nancumprod"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the cumulative product of tensor elements over a given axis "
"treating Not a Numbers (NaNs) as one.  The cumulative product does not "
"change when NaNs are encountered and leading NaNs are replaced by ones."
msgstr ""
"返回给定轴上张量元素的累积乘积，将非数字（NaN）视为1。遇到 NaN 时累积乘积"
"不会改变，前导的 NaN 会被替换为1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:5 of
msgid "Ones are returned for slices that are all-NaN or empty."
msgstr "对于全部为 NaN 或空的切片，返回1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:7 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:9 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the cumulative product is computed.  By default the "
"input is flattened."
msgstr "计算累积乘积的轴。默认情况下，输入会被展平。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:12 of
msgid ""
"Type of the returned tensor, as well as of the accumulator in which the "
"elements are multiplied.  If *dtype* is not specified, it defaults to the"
" dtype of `a`, unless `a` has an integer dtype with a precision less than"
" that of the default platform integer.  In that case, the default "
"platform integer is used instead."
msgstr ""
"返回张量的类型，以及元素相乘时使用的累加器类型。如果未指定 *dtype*，则"
"默认为 `a` 的 dtype，除非 `a` 是精度低于默认平台整数的整数类型。在这种"
"情况下，将使用默认平台整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:18 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape and buffer length as the expected output but the type of the "
"resulting values will be cast if necessary."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。它必须具有与预期输出相同的形状和缓冲区长度，"
"但必要时结果值的类型将被转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:23 of
msgid ""
"**nancumprod** -- A new array holding the result is returned unless `out`"
" is specified, in which case it is returned."
msgstr ""
"**nancumprod** -- 返回一个包含结果的新数组，除非指定了 `out`，此时返回 `"
"out`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.cumprod`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:30 of
msgid "Cumulative product across array propagating NaNs."
msgstr "对数组进行累积乘积运算，并传播 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nancumprod.nancumprod:33 of
msgid "Show which elements are NaN."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是 NaN。"

